    <div class="alpheios-lex-entry" lemma-id="n657" body-key="α">
          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἄμαξα, ἅμαξα</span></b>  (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἅμα, ἄξων</span>): fourwheeled draught
            <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">wagon</span>, distinguished from the war - chariot (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἅρμα</span>), which had two wheels, <i><span class="en">Od. 9.251</span></i>; also the constellation of the
          Great Bear (<span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">the Wain</span>), <i><span class="en">Il.
            18.487</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Od.
          5.273</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
